WEBVTT

1
00:01:40.934 --> 00:01:43.728
World markets posted
record gains today.

2
00:01:43.729 --> 00:01:48.025
with demand for batteries and
pharmaceuticals leading the way...

3
00:09:09.383 --> 00:09:10.842
You catch more flies with honey.

4
00:09:10.843 --> 00:09:13.135
Who are you right now?

5
00:09:13.136 --> 00:09:16.265
An Algerian or a Frenchman?

6
00:10:19.995 --> 00:10:20.996
No. it's an invitation.

7
00:24:12.786 --> 00:24:14.120
I'm impressed.

8
00:24:14.121 --> 00:24:15.788
You speak very well.

9
00:24:15.789 --> 00:24:18.333
A lot of my fans speak it.

10
00:24:21.128 --> 00:24:22.421
Does he?

11
00:30:27.995 --> 00:30:29.495
<i>Thank you. Doctor.</i>

12
00:30:29.496 --> 00:30:32.749
I'm sorry I don't
have better news.
